ickson\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"tally\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"WordPress Self Hosted\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"http://thisismyurl.com/?p=81\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:231:\"I\'m always strugging to fine easy short codes to make my WordPress experience even better and this week, I had an opportunity to write a new short code for thisismyurl.com that would allow me to add a tutorial count to my homepage.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Christopher Ross\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1696:\"<p>I&#8217;m always strugging to fine easy short codes to make my WordPress experience even better and this week, I had an opportunity to write a new short code for thisismyurl.com that would allow me to add a tutorial count to my homepage.</p>\n<p>The idea came to me while surfing the amazingly talented <a href=\"http://www.billerickson.net/\" target=\"_blank\">Bill Erickson&#8217;s website</a>, which was recently redesigned and now features a tally of his total WordPress tutorials. I&#8217;d be lying if I said I haven&#8217;t always been jealous of some of his features so this weekend I wrote a quick WordPress short code to display my own tutorial count.</p>\n<pre>\nadd_shortcode( \'count_tutorials\', \'thisismyurl_get_category_count\' );\nfunction thisismyurl_get_category_count( $category = NULL, $maxposts = 5000, $number_format = true ) {\n\nif ( $category ) {\n\n$args = array( \'numberposts\' =&gt; $maxposts , \'category\' =&gt; $category );\n$get_tutorials = get_posts( $args );\n\nif ( $number_format )\n$get_tutorials = number_format( count( $get_tutorials ) );\nelse\n$get_tutorials = count( $get_tutorials );\n\nreturn $get_tutorials;\n\n} else {\n\nreturn NULL;\n\n}\n\n}\n</pre>\n<p>Since it&#8217;s written as a short code, you can add it to your WordPress posts and pages or call it from the template.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/sA9TPOakIeOfUUB1Pb9OpuSrsHg/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/sA9TPOakIeOfUUB1Pb9OpuSrsHg/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/sA9TPOakIeOfUUB1Pb9OpuSrsHg/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/sA9TPOakIeOfUUB1Pb9OpuSrsHg/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"http://thisismyurl.com/81/get-a-category-count-in-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:2:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:79:\"http://thisismyurl.com/files/2012/10/thisismyurl_get_category_count-300x120.jpg\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\