 spruce up your website and give credit for your feature images.</p>\n<p>Here&#8217;s the code snippet I use on thisismyurl.com:</p>\n<pre>\nif ( thisismyurl_has_custom_media_field() ) {\n\n$credit_name = thisismyurl_get_custom_media_field( get_post_thumbnail_id( $post-&amp;gt;ID ), &#039;credit_name&#039; );\n$credit_url = thisismyurl_get_custom_media_field( get_post_thumbnail_id( $post-&amp;gt;ID ), &#039;credit_url&#039; );\n\nif ( empty( $credit_name ) )\n$credit_name = $credit_url;\n\nif ( !empty( $credit_url ) )\n$credit_text = &#039;&lt;a title=&quot;&#039; . $credit_name . &#039;&quot; href=&quot;&#039; . $credit_url . &#039;&quot;&gt;&#039; . $credit_name . &#039;&lt;/a&gt;&#039;;\nelse\n$credit_text = $credit_name;\n\n$credit_text = &#039;\n&lt;div class=&quot;media-credit&quot;&gt;&#039; . $credit_text . &#039;&lt;/div&gt;\n&#039;;\n\necho $credit_text;\n}\n</pre>\n<p>Add this code to your single.php file and if you create a <strong>Unique ID</strong> called <em>credit_name</em> and <em>credit_url</em> in the plugin admin, you&#8217;ll see a nifty photo credit appear under your featured images.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/voL3jycK8b91vr9Lx3M-sEnys0E/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/voL3jycK8b91vr9Lx3M-sEnys0E/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a><br/>\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/voL3jycK8b91vr9Lx3M-sEnys0E/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/voL3jycK8b91vr9Lx3M-sEnys0E/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a></p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"http://thisismyurl.com/8647/add-photo-credit-featured-image-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1: