('94565', '_transient_rss_8c8c1f01f7f8848cf21bccc5ca076c29', 'O:9:\"MagpieRSS\":19:{s:6:\"parser\";i:0;s:12:\"current_item\";a:0:{}s:5:\"items\";a:10:{i:0;a:14:{s:5:\"title\";s:55:\"Starting June 10, 2010, Full Hiatus (Support, Upgrades)\";s:4:\"link\";s:53:\"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Viadat/~3/-6Zv_OthqNg/\";s:8:\"comments\";s:68:\"http://www.viadat.com/2010/06/full-hiatus-support-upgrades/#comments\";s:7:\"pubdate\";s:31:\"Sat, 05 Jun 2010 02:49:37 +0000\";s:2:\"dc\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";s:5:\"admin\";}s:8:\"category\";s:54:\"AnnouncementTranslationsWordpress Store Locator Plugin\";s:4:\"guid\";s:28:\"http://www.viadat.com/?p=951\";s:11:\"description\";s:409:\"Store Locator\n** ON HIATUS (on a break) ** NOT DEAD **\n&#160;\nStarting Thursday, June 10, 2010 &#8230; \nUnavailable:\n\nUpgrade purchases (addons &#038; themes) will become unavailable.\nEmail &#038; forum support for any new issues related to base Store Locator unavailable (please view: Documentation &#124; Answers already in the forum)\n\nTentative Plans:\n\nUpdates that have been in the works for several [...]\";s:7:\"content\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";s:5832:\"<div style=\'text-align:center; background-color:LightYellow; border:solid gold 1px; padding:7px; font-weight:bold\'>Store Locator<br />\n** ON <a href=\"http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/hiatus\" target=\'_blank\'>HIATUS</a> <i>(on a break)</i> ** NOT DEAD **</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Thursday, June 10, 2010 &#8230; </strong></p>\n<h3>Unavailable:</h3>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/products-page/\">Upgrade purchases</a> (addons &#038; themes) will become unavailable.</li>\n<li>Email &#038; forum support for any new issues related to base Store Locator unavailable (please view: <a href=\"http://docs.viadat.com/\">Documentation</a> | <a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/store-locator/forum/\">Answers already in the forum</a>)</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Tentative Plans:</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Updates that have been in the works for s