g some exciting features.  </p>\n<p>Additionally, to allow for quicker development, addons will be unavailable <em><strong>starting Friday, Oct. 30rd, 2009</strong></em> &#8212; this will allow improvements to the addon system, and 100% focus on development of new features (many of which we hope to be a surprise), since support is always provided for addons.  Themes will still be available however.</p>\n<p><strong>In the Meantime&#8230;</strong></p>\n<p>1) Continue submitting your suggestions &#8212; You can do so in the comment section</p>\n<p>2) More translations still needed &#8212; you can use this translation template to get started: <strong><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/vdl/translation-template.1.2.40.zip\" >Translation Template &#8211; As of v1.2.41</a> </strong>.</p>\n<p>&#8230; to make translating easier, will most likely set up a dedicated page for translations, so that everyone can see who made the specific translations and also so people can collaborate.</p>\n<p><strong><a  href=\'http://www.viadat.com/store-locator/\'>Go to the Store Locator Download Page</a></strong></p>\n<div id=\"crp_related\"><p>Â </p><p>Â </p><h2>Related Posts:</h2><ul><li style=\'padding-bottom:5px\'><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/2009/01/wordpress-store-locator-v11-happy-new-year-french-translation/\" rel=\"bookmark\" class=\"crp_title\">Google Maps Store Locator for Wordpress v1.1 + HAPPY NEW YEAR! + French Translation</a></li><li style=\'padding-bottom:5px\'><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/2009/06/new-things-to-see-since-version-1223-version-13-is-approaching/\" rel=\"bookmark\" class=\"crp_title\">New Things to See Since Version 1.2.23 + Version 1.3 is Approaching</a></li><li style=\'padding-bottom:5px\'><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/2010/04/no-new-customizations-temporarily/\" rel=\"bookmark\" class=\"crp_title\">Temporary Customization Request Hiatus After Friday, April 30, 2010</a></li><li style=\'padding-bottom:5px\'><a href=\"http://www.viadat.com/2009/01/wordpress-s