('196', '9', '2011-08-05 19:55:41', '2011-08-05 19:55:41', 'Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) producer VicNRG, maker of Victory Blue DEF, has begun production of DEF for Cummins Filtration at its plant in Fort Worth, Texas.\r\n\r\nJason Lower, Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer of VicNRG, told discoverDEF.com: \"We\'re very excited to work with Cummins.  Earning their trust and confidence by demonstrating our ability to produce the highest quality DEF available is justification for all the hard work and dedication of the Victory Team.\r\n\r\n\"The fact that Victory is trusted by OEMs is proof that the care and attention given to both our process and our service has paid off.  Victory excelled during the Production Part Approval Process (PPAP) evaluation conducted by Cummins.  There is no doubt that this success lends tremendous credibility to our operation.\"\r\n\r\nThe facility in Fort Worth has the capability to fill trucks, rail cars and to decant DEF into both totes and packaged products. VicNRG is constructing several other blending plants in strategic locations across the country, which will be announced on discoverDEF.com shortly.\r\n\r\nVicNRG\'s Victory Blue DEF brand is API registered.', 'VicNRG begins DEF production for Cummins', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '151-revision-6', '', '', '2011-08-05 19:55:41', '2011-08-05 19:55:41', '', '151', 'http://www.victorybluedef.com/2011/08/05/151-revision-6/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
('197', '9', '2011-08-08 16:08:44', '2011-08-08 16:08:44', '<em>Jun 27, 2011 -Â </em>\r\n\r\nVictory Blue Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) manufacturer VicNRG has began DEF production for automotive products distributor Valvoline.\r\n\r\nShipments of drums and totes from VicNRG\'s Fort Worth, TX, facility started in early May, immediately following the finalization of the agreement between the two companies.\r\n\r\nJason Lower, Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer of VicNRG, told discoverDEF.com: \"Our team has worked tirelessly to earn credibility and gain the trust of industry leaders. We continue to prove that attention to detail and superior customer service yield unparalleled results. This is evidenced by the fact that we have captured the attention of OEM\'s and internationally recognized companies like Cummins and Valvoline.\r\n\r\n\"VicNRG continues to expand its network of production facilities in order to provide quality product where our customers need it most. These facilities offer our customers bulk DEF 24/7 using automated systems - one example of how Victory Blue is taking customer service to the next level.\"\r\n\r\nVicNRG\'s DEF production facilities have the capability to fill rail cars, bulk truckloads and to decant DEF into totes, drums and packaged products. The company is constructing several new blending plants in strategic locations across the country. The openings of these plants will be announced on discoverDEF.com shortly.\r\n\r\nIn May VicNRG announced it had started DEF production for Cummins.\r\n\r\nVicNRG\'s Victory BlueDEF brand is API registered.', 'VicNRG begins DEF production for Valvoline', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'vicnrg-begins-def-production-for-valvoline', '', '', '2011-08-09 14:55:42', '2011-08-09 14:55:42', '', '0', 'http://www.victorybluedef.com/?p=197', '0', 'post', '', '0'),
