hese standards is to use SCR and DEF.  Daimler, PACCAR, Volvo, Mack, Isuzu, Hino, Ford, GM, Navistar, AGCO, Case, John Deere, and others are using SCR,\r\n\r\nSCR technology offers many benefits, most importantly great fuel efficiency. On top of this, owners of SCR vehicles and equipment will enjoy greater reliability and a longer oil change interval, all of which adds up to impressive savings over the life of the vehicle.\r\n', 'New Diesel Exhaust Fluid (DEF) facility in Stockton, CA. ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '306-revision-5', '', '', '2013-03-08 09:30:14', '2013-03-08 15:30:14', '', '306', 'http://www.govictoryblue.com/2013/03/08/306-revision-5/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
